videos.headline: Texas State strikes first with a 66-yad TD
videos.description: Brock Sturges takes the short pass from Tyler Witt and takes it 66 yards to the house for touchdown. (edited)

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas State strikes first with a 66-yad TD) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris keeps it himself for UTSA touchdown
videos.description: QB Frank Harris fakes the hand off to find the open gap and rushes in for a 17-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris keeps it himself for UTSA touchdown) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: UTSA's Harris scores his second TD of game
videos.description: Frank Harris drags a defender with him as he pushes through to score a 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UTSA's Harris scores his second TD of game) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisdom comes up with the 81-yard pick-6
videos.description: Rashad Wisdom extends UTSA's lead as he picks off Tyler Vitt's pass and runs it back 81 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisdom comes up with the 81-yard pick-6) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cephus makes an unbeliveable TD catch
videos.description: Joshua Cephus finds a way to break free from the defender long enough to make the one-handed 25-yard touchdown catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cephus makes an unbeliveable TD catch) 2020/09/12 ESHEET
